    law_category: "labor",
    article_num: "86",
    text: "The regular and extraordinary termination of the employment contract must be expressed in written form. The employer must provide a written explanation of the actual reason for termination of the employment contract. Upon termination, the employer must notify the employee in writing of the legal protection available and of the rights arising from unemployment insurance and the obligation to register in the records of job seekers.",
